Subject: Re: [VB] Disc brakes for buses

"Wide 5" refers to the lug pattern on a '70 and earlier bus and pre '68 Bug. '71 buses went to a smaller diameter 5 lug pattern and '68 model bugs had a 4 lug pattern.
 
